          <title>Shohei Ohtani homers as the Dodgers rout the Mets 8-0 for a 2-1 lead in the NLCS</title>
          <description><![CDATA[NEW YORK (AP) — By the time Shohei Ohtani stepped to the plate in the eighth inning Wednesday night, the Los Angeles Dodgers were already in control. Once the ball left his bat, Game 3 of the National League Championship Series was over.]]></description>
